{"tid":398174,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國算唔算係全世界最無恥嘅國家?","createTime":"2017-09-13T03:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T00:21:47.000Z","uid":143499,"like":488,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6771141d0076e7b6d0f955f0260c7598acbfdf8","tid":398174,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:51:25.000Z","msg":"先唔講佢地喺運動界嘅威水史，係歷史上泡菜支那一直飾演過橋抽板，扮可憐嘅角色。<br />\n<br />\n當年朝鮮兵違抗軍令，喺南京玩大咗，導致日本要消滅證據，造成大屠殺。佢地甚至比當年嘅日本兵更殘暴不仁，手法更血腥。不過戰後就扮好人、扮受害者， 有乜嘢資格追討賠償？<br />\n<br />\n另外一單就係韓戰，已經敗走台灣嘅國民黨政府在人道及軍事上支援南韓，但係之後南韓喺UN嘅會議上否認中華民國嘅地位,仲要為咗討好土共,自我閹割,喺日後嘅韓國主辦國際賽事唔畀台灣用青天白日滿地紅旗。<br />\n<br />\n除咗歷史外，仲有政治制度、社會經濟體系、文化及抄襲等問題，泡菜支那根本上係一個最低劣嘅民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2689e08afc16b29e2eae6762bc0c98c8bd02bb","tid":398174,"uid":90704,"like":134,"dislike":6,"score":128,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:52:38.000Z","msg":"問過_国未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27c79d6e17f64f36302364bb0e913a702778830","tid":398174,"uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:46:34.000Z","msg":"推到D泡狗人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b282c29a50fd2e761a5ccea8f7aa1b82f7a463eb","tid":398174,"uid":143499,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:47:56.000Z","msg":"崇韓撚入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7dd5e3e83e85650853a67d2588b99675e63005c","tid":398174,"uid":124991,"like":11,"dislike":8,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:49:22.000Z","msg":"起馬唔係「最」"},{"pid":"c5574ebe6de8aac7a677d167ad254e5ad8559766","tid":398174,"uid":18241,"like":124,"dislike":8,"score":116,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起馬唔係「最」</blockquote><br />\n冠軍: 支國<br />\n亞軍: 泡菜國<br />\n季軍: 印